IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
User italoamaya03@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass email/italoamaya03@gmail.com"

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Personal/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Personal/Mail/gmail/Inbox
